---
title: No Fuss Bacon, Chicken & Pesto Orecchiette with Baby Leaves & Parmesan Cheese
description: Presenting a few of our favourite things: rich tomato sauce, bacon, Parmesan cheese and basil pesto. All of those deep flavours meld
together wonderfully when tossed through al dente orecchiette. This'll be bumped up to a champion household dinner in no time!

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with orecchiette due to local
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
